# GitHub Personal Access Token (classic) or fine-grained token with read access to public data.
# Used for GraphQL API calls to https://api.github.com/graphql when loading pinned repositories.
# Classic token: include the `read:user` scope so the API can resolve your profile and pinned items reliably.
# Fine-grained: grant read-only metadata (and repository contents if needed) as appropriate.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
